sts: 619<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/26/03 10:52 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Plane of Torment</span><hr size=1> it's not that bad with a good group, better than tier 1 but not as good as tier 2, sort of like poi for tier 2 <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=89629" target="top"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Master Delaregar Stormtamer<br>
