</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=istari@graffeswizardcompilation>Istari</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br>  Posts: 435<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/27/03 12:29 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Plane of Torment</span><hr size=1> before they opened the zone to the public(awhile ago) i quadded blood ravens there and noted 2% aaxp per kill. this was when pos frogs were still giving 8%, and were of a similar HP amount. it is really awful, and is more of a raid zone than anything. I think the xp mod is to discourage people from just regularly grouping at the spots for the saryrn key and getting it without having to REALLY hate that camp. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=whizbangdustyboots>Whizbang Dustyboots</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elder Arcanist<BR>Gnomus Originalus</span><br>  Posts: 13543<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/27/03 12:34 am)</font><br>     <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Plane of Torment</span><hr size=1> Given the chain add fun further in, this really merits a higher XP bonus than it has.<br>
